    {"id":"preview-note","type":"text","x":60,"y":715,"width":800,"height":14,"text":"⚠ 关键: const [isPreview, setIsPreview] = useState(false) — 编辑/预览同一state，isPreview切换时只隐藏编辑UI，canvasItems+filters不变","fontSize":10,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#FAAD14"}
